<p>The data on this page comes from the County of Santa Clara legislative portal:</p>
<ul>
  <li>
    <code>sccgov.iqm2.com</code>
    <ul>
      <li>
        The IQM2 (Accela Legislative Management, a Granicus product) portal that
        hosts County of Santa Clara Board of Supervisors agendas, legislative
        files, agenda items, and public meeting documents. It is the source for
        meetings, matters, and attachment metadata, and the host that attachment
        links point to.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>
<p>
  The County publishes attachment PDFs directly, so Civic Gallery downloads each
  one, extracts its text, and generates summaries automatically. Every
  attachment still links back to its official source on the portal.
</p>
